   The Lighthouse Cafe, 362 Periwinkle Way, (239) 472-0303, is known
for its hearty breakfasts featuring omelets, frittatas and hotcakes,
$5-$10.

   "When it's Teacher Appreciation Week, we get something every day;
we feel very appreciated by our parents," said the 62-year-old
Camarillo resident.
